contents.description: 30 Days Of JavaScript challenge has been started on 1 January and ended on 30 January 2020. It is of the best JavaScript material on the internet. Students learned quite a lot of concepts. I hope this will help lots of students. JavaScript for Ever!

contents.description: 30 Days Of Python challenge has been started on 22 November 2019 and ended on 22 December 2020. It is of the best references for Pythonistas, data scientists, and aspiring ML. Students learned quite a lot of concepts. Python is eating the world
